description: Transcendent Group AB engages in the provision of management consulting business services. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2019-10-22. The firm offers management consulting services, including compliance, corporate governance, digital governance, information security, internal audit, Information Technology (IT) audit, data protection advice and risk management, among others. The Company’s clients operate in both the public and private sectors, including government agencies, businesses and other organizations in a variety of industries. The firm has offices in Sweden, Norway, Denmark, Finland, the Netherlands, Belgium, Lithuania and Germany.
